    - rid: 107151343762276446
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276447
          output: "The Beholder is with us! Our man utterly humiliated this so-called
            \u201Corator.\u201D He exposed the fallacies of his arguments and proved
            to all that he is naught but a charlatan. The commoners themselves drove
            him from the plaza with kicks and jeers. It is doubtful he will show
            his face again, and better still, our man inherited his audience!\r\n[Gained
            30 Zeal]"
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276448
          output: 'What a disgrace! Our man was utterly undone by the rival''s rhetoric
            and logic. The humiliation was such that by the time it ended, the crowd
            was roaring with laughter at his expense. We have been defeated, and
            the blow to our sect''s morale is heavy.

            [Lost 30 Zeal]'
